    bibo:volume "317" ;
    dc:creator "Ayrey, Richard F.; Myers, Brandon T." ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Description of the male of Wernerius mumai (Sissom 1993) from western Arizona with data on reproduction (Scorpiones Vaejovidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4648737>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4648727>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4648729>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4648731>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4648739>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4648733>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4648735> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4648737>
    dc:description "Figures 18–20: Wernerius mumai. Figure 18. Habitat, Gold Road, Arizona. Figure 19. Microhabitat. Figure 20. Topotype female with newborns." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4648737/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4648727>
    dc:description "Figures 1–2. Wernerius mumai adult (1) and subadult (2) topotype males in vivo habitus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4648727/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4648729>
    dc:description "Figures 3–4: Wernerius mumai. Figure 3. Topotype female in vivo habitus. Figure 4. Topotype male in dorsal (4a) and ventral 4(b) views. Scale bar, 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4648729/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4648731>
    dc:description "Figures 5–11: Wernerius mumai, topotype male. Figure 5. Carapace. Figure 6. Pectines. Figure 7. Telson in lateral (7a) and dorsal (7b) views. Figure 8. Telson, lateral view, close-up of aculeus and subaculear tubercle. Figure 9. Metasoma V, ventral view. Figure 10. Chela fixed (10a) and movable (10b) fingers dentition. Figure 11. Metasoma and telson in ventral (11a), dorsal (11b), and lateral (11c) views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4648731/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4648739>
    dc:description "Figure 21. Wernerius mumai topotype male, trichobothrial pattern. Chela external (21a), ventral (21b), and internal (21c) views. Femur dorsal (21d) view. Patella dorsal (21e), external (21f), and ventral (21g) views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4648739/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4648733>
    dc:description "Figures 12–15: Wernerius mumai, topotype male, legs. Figure 12. Right legs I–IV, prolateral view. Figure 13. Right telotarsus III, ventral view. Figure 14. Left leg III, showing femur, patella, tibia, and lack of basitarsus and full telotarsus. Figure 15. Left leg III, close-up of leg anomaly showing the apotele growing directly from tibia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4648733/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4648735>
    dc:description "Figures 16–17: Wernerius mumai, topotype male. Figure 16. Hemispermatophore, dorsal (16a) and ventral (16d) views, close-up of distal tip (16b), and close-up of embedded mating plug (16c). Figure 17. Mating plug in dorsal (17a), internal (17b), ventral (17c), and external (17d) views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4648735/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

